channel.title: Null's Object ID List 83-205 (Like 185 is a wall) (Help thread, not request)
channel.description:
Hiya. I have noticed that Nulls as objects are just objects you cant right click on. Well, I added a bunch of nulls and made a list to describe them to help people. And, I also learned things myself. This list includes the null IDs of 83-205. You will have view it from my website, because it will eventually exceed 20000 characters. Here's the link. Use this well!
[url=http://www.freewebs.com/linscape/Null%20Object%20IDs.txt]http://www.freewebs.com/linscape/Null%20Object%20IDs.txt[/url]
~Lin
[glow=black,2,300]PS:Please post feedback, because I would like to see if this helps people. If I dont get feedback, I guess I wont post them... [/glow]
